  "description": "<p><p><strong>Role: Outdoor Sales Executive</strong><br /><strong>Industry: Engineering</strong><br /><strong>Location: Joo Koon</strong><br /><strong>5.5 days | Mon to Fri 830am-530pm, Sat 830am - 1230pm (Alt Sat work)</strong><br /><strong>Basic $2800 to $3200 + $1400 Transport Allowances + Commissions</strong><br /><br /><strong>Reequipment: </strong><br /><strong>Posses with valid class 3 license and own vehicle</strong></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Outdoor sales role in meeting clients or customers in promoting company's product.</li><li>Conduct calls and face-to-face meetings with customers daily.</li><li>Build and maintain relationships with new and repeat customers.</li><li>Maintain records of all sales leads and customer accounts.</li><li>Educate customers on how products or services can benefit them financially and professionally.</li></ul><p>Tai Jia Seng Reg No: R26159755</p><p>The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p></p>",
